query:
UPDATE entries
                    SET
                        activity_id = $1,
                        parent_id = $2,
                        frac_index = $3,
                        display_as_sets = $4,
                        is_sequence = $5,
                        start_time = $6,
                        end_time = $7,
                        duration_ms = $8
                    WHERE id = $9
